			<h3>Schemin'</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>Start: discard all bullet cards</li>
				<li>End: keep some, discard the rest</li>
				<li>Play a card or draw 3.</li>
				<li>or fetch Brilliant Idea (Marshal & Prisoners).</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
		<div class="table-cell tc-6">
			<h3>Stealin'</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>Actions are mandatory.</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

