<h3>Actions</h3>
<ul>
	<li>Move: 1 inside train, up to 3 on roof</li>
	<li>Fire
		<ul>
			<li>cannot shoot someone in your location</li>
			<li>distance 1 inside train, no limit on roof but subject to line of sight</li>
			<li>bullet cards go on top of a player's deck</li>
		</ul>
	</li>
	<li>Punch
		<ul>
			<li>puncher chooses what to drop</li>
			<li>purses are chosen at random, placed without looking</li>
		</ul>
	</li>
	<li>Ride
		<ul>
			<li>Only resolves if bandit is aligned with a horse.</li>
			<li>Can jump on a horse either from roof or inside train.</li>
			<li>Move 0-3 cars.</li>
			<li>Place bandit inside adjacent an adjacent train car or stagecoach.</li>
		</ul>
	</li>
	<li>Brilliant Idea
		<ul>
			<li>New action: add Brilliant Idea to hand from discard or deck.</li>
			<li>Not in/on prison car roof/corridor/cell: copy last bandit action other than Brilliant Idea.
				<ul>
					<li>Ignore Marshal's bullet penalties.</li>
					<li>Can copy shoot/punch during special Jarring turns</li>
				</ul>
			</li>
			<li>In prison cell: move to roof or corridor.</li>
			<li>Prison roof/corridor:
				<ul>
					<li>take a prisoner card, max 1 - cannot choose this if already have a prisoner card.</li>
					<li>free another bandit, move that bandit to your space and he gives you 1 loot of his choice.</li>
				</ul>
			</li>
		</ul>
</ul>

<br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br />

<h3>Stagecoach</h3>
<p>At end of round, move stagecoach one car toward caboose, unless already aligned with caboose.</p>
<ul>
	<li>Inside
		<ul>
			<li>Enter with Ride, or with Floor Change from stagecoach roof.</li>
			<li>Considered adjacent to the interior of its aligned train car for Fire and Punch.</li>
			<li>Marshal never enters stagecoach.</li>
			<li>When entering for first time, must take a hostage (max 1).</li>
		</ul>
	</li>
	<li>Roof
		<ul>
			<li>Enter with Move from train roof, or with Floor Change from stagecoach interior.</li>
			<li>Considered adjacent to the roof of its aligned train car for Move, Fire, and Punch.</li>
			<li>Bandits on roof can shoot any bandit on the train's roof, and vice versa.</li>
		</ul>
	</li>
	<li>Shotgun
		<ul>
			<li>Guards strongbox, idle until punched.</li>
			<li>Release the strongbox by punching Shotgun, moving him to the roof of the aligned car.</li>
			<li>Take a neutral bullet if on Shotgun's location, then move to an adjacent car's roof (not stagecoach).</li>
			<li>Shotgun blocks line of sight, but not when firing from stagecoach.</li>
			<li>Shotgun is always aligned with the stagecoach.</li>
		</ul>
	</li>
</ul>

<h3>Prison Car</h3>
<ul>
	<li>Cannot choose to enter cell.</li>
	<li>Cannot shoot/punch a captured bandit.</li>
	<li>Cannot move a bandit into a cell with shoot/punch.</li>
	<li>Brilliant Idea is the only action that will resolve for captured bandits.</li>
</ul>

<h3>Prisoners</h3>
<ul>
	<li>Max 1 prisoner per bandit.</li>
	<li>Trusty sidekick: take 2 loot takens with Rob action.</li>
	<li>Not trusty sidekick: gain power of corresponding bandit.</li>
</ul>

<h3>Marshal</h3>
<ul>
	<li>Bandits can punch/shoot Marshal and move into his location.</li>
	<li>Punch Marshal - take a Brawler card.</li>
	<li>Goals
		<ul>
			<li>Add a new goal to current goal zone each round.</li>
			<li>Marshal wins by completing 4 goals.</li>
		</ul>
	<li>Actions
		<ul>
			<li>Move+ and Floor Change+
				<ul>
					<li>Play an additional card.</li>
					<li>Can be chained.</li>
					<li>Bonus play only triggers on standard turns.</li>
					<li>Cannot draw cards with bonus play.</li>
				</ul>
			<li>Capture
				<ul>
					<li>Send a bandit in his location to the prison cell.</li>
					<li>Take bandit's wanted poster, never loses it.</li>
					<li>Can capture a bandit multiple times per game.</li>
				</ul>
			</li>
			<li>Shoot
				<ul>
					<li>Can shoot twice if 2+ bandits are available - one card from each pile.</li>
					<li>Cannot shoot the same bandit twice - choose either pile.</li>
				</ul>
			</li>
		</ul>
	</li>
	<li>Modified Events
		<ul>
			<li>Angry Marshal: Resolve 1 shoot action, then resolve 1 move action.</li>
			<li>A Shot of Whiskey...: Take flask on this location, may use it like a bandit.
				<ul>
					<li>Marshal never drops whiskey.</li>
					<li>Old Whiskey: Ignore bonus plays, 2 action cards maximum.</li>
				</ul>
			</li>
			<li>Marshal's Revenge: Affects bandits in Marshal's location too.</li>
		</ul>
	</li>
	<li>End Game
		<ul>
			<li>Remaining prisoner cards are added to achievement zone.</li>
			<li>Any mailbag on the train is added to achievement zone.</li>
		</ul>
	</li>
</ul>








